    {
      "id": 6702,
      "name": "OpenShift Application Delivery",
      "description": "Application Delivery header",
      "type": "text",
      "theme": "newSolidGray",
      "interval": 5,
      "timescale": "day",
      "displaySettings": {},
      "content": "<h2>OpenShift Application Delivery</h2><p>App-owner view of how workloads reach the cluster: GitOps sync status (ArgoCD fleet + controllers + repo + grpc server) and KubeVirt (VM inventory, running state, virt components, live migration activity).</p><p><strong>Sections:</strong> ArgoCD app inventory &middot; ArgoCD sync &amp; controller performance &middot; ArgoCD repo &amp; server &middot; KubeVirt cluster &middot; KubeVirt components &middot; Active delivery alerts</p><p><strong>Source:</strong> PromQL queries via Thanos Querier. Auto-binds via categories <code>OpenShift_GitOps</code> and <code>OpenShift_KubeVirt</code>.</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 6703,
      "name": "ArgoCD Total Apps",
      "description": "Total ArgoCD applications across all GitOps fleets",
      "type": "bigNumber",
      "theme": "newSolidDarkBlue",
      "interval": 5,
      "timescale": "day",
      "displaySettings": {},
      "bigNumberInfo": {
        "dataPoints": [
          {
            "deviceGroupFullPath": "*",
            "deviceDisplayName": "*",
            "dataSourceFullName": "ArgoCD Sync Overview (ArgoCD_Sync_Overview)",
            "instanceName": "*",
            "dataPointName": "total_apps",
            "name": "total_apps",
            "aggregateFunction": "sum"
          }
        ],
        "virtualDataPoints": [],
        "counters": [],
        "bigNumberItems": [
          {
